=======
Changes
=======

0.2.0 (*unreleased*)
====================

- Project revived, requires Python 3.12+ (3.13 supported)
- Test discovery and filtering by keyword (`-k`)
- Exit on first failure (`-x`)
- Disable output capturing (`-s`)
- Code coverage (`--cov`)
- Sort tests by their definition order
- Async test validation
- Warning collection and reporting
- Improved CLI with proper exit codes and conditional `ipdb` support
- Set `TEST_RUNNER=rut` environment variable

0.1.0 (*2022-04-29*)
====================

- minimal test runner